2398: _{l}ym~ and {l}ith_; 750: _{L}ytyAEsAEs and {m}ykyAEsAEs, {l}ese and
{m}ore_; 1899: _That was {l}ord of aAEsAEs that {l}ond_; 2152: _Loo,
{l}ordys of euery {l}ond_; 2375: _With aAEsAEs {m}aner of {m}ynstralsye_;
149: _He reynyd hys {st}ed vnto a {st}ake_; 1065: _{W}aytes on the
{w}aAEsAEs gan blowe_; 13: _{w}ater and {w}ynde_.

_b._ In the same way abstract ideas are connected, so far as they belong
