  aEuro~This reeve sat vpon a ful good stot,
  That was al {pomely gray}, and highte Scot.aEuro(TM)

p. 27, l. 744. Cf. l. 788. On _St. James_ cf. KA�lbingaEuro(TM)s note to _Am. and
