p. 34, l. 954 ff. Cf. _Tristrem_, l. 1409 ff.:

  aEuro~Out of Deuelin toun
  Aze folk wel fast ran,
  In a water to droun,
  So ferd were A3/4ai A3/4an.aEuro(TM)

p. 34, l. 963 f. Cf. _Beves of Hamtoun_, l. 187 f.:

