p. 38, l. 1076. Cf. _Ipomadon_, l. 239 f.:

  aEuro~Tyll vncovth contreys will I wende,
  The maner wille I see.aEuro(TM)

p. 39, l. 1081. _is_ was to be corrected into _it_: aEuro~Because you slew
him that possessedA it.aEuro(TM)

p. 39, l. 1086. This line, according to HallaEuro(TM)s emendation, means: You
