p. 41, l. 1144. As to a man riding into the hall, cf. SkeataEuro(TM)s note to
ChauceraEuro(TM)s _SquiereaEuro(TM)s Tale_, l. 80, and KA�lbingaEuro(TM)s note to _Ipomadon_
