p. 49, l. 1395. _fend_ = _defend_; cf. ZupitzaaEuro(TM)s note to _Guy_, l. 576.

p. 51, l. 1443 f. As the existence of _fede_ = _fode_, aEuro~fellowaEuro(TM) is
